description:
Generate a status report for all feeds in the Emoncms system and save it to /home/ga/emoncms_status_report.json. The report must include the total feed count and a list of all feeds with their ID, name, tag, latest value, unit, and engine.

Required JSON structure:
{
  "report_title": "Emoncms System Status Report",
  "total_feeds": <integer>,
  "feeds": [
    {
      "id": <integer>,
      "name": "<string>",
      "tag": "<string>",
      "value": <number or null>,
      "unit": "<string>",
      "engine": <integer>
    }
  ]
}
